#List of everything I trip over

Finding when you first logged on to a computer "last" lists user logins in reverse order
Set alias for ssh targets in ~/.ssh like:
  Host aliasname
    HostName realhostname.domain
    User username

comment blocks of code in vim:
  Ctrl+V for VISUAL BLOCK mode
  select the lines
  Shift+I for insert, then hit the comment character you want to insert
  ESC, takes a second, then inserts
